description: SmartDisk's titanium USB 2X floppy disk drive brings more functionality and versatility to your USB-equipped Macintosh or PC computer. The drive reads and writes standard 1.44 MB floppy disks and has a fast data transfer rates, and is powered through the USB port, so does not need an AC adapter. And the sleek, titanium design matches perfectly with the new PowerBook G4, and the Sony Vaio.
title: Verbatim SmartDisk Titanium 2x USB 2.0 External Floppy Disk Drive FDUSB-TM2
